items.title: The Home Depot Announces Exclusive KILZ® Brand Agreement
items.description: The Home Depot and Behr Paint Company have expanded their long-term relationship to exclusively offer KILZ® branded primer products in the United States and Puerto Rico. The Home Depot will become the only home improvement big box retailer to offer KILZ® branded primer products including KILZ Original®, KILZ PVA®, KILZ 2®, KILZ 3 Premium®, KILZ Restoration® and KILZ Mold & Mildew® and more problem-solving primer products and aerosols.
